{"tid":1492124,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"關於開學排斥警察仔女問題","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T09:34:00.000Z","uid":144594,"like":85,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c206afc73cd0e69c2176b96f25a968d8f3359302","tid":1492124,"uid":144594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"好多人都好糾結應唔應該禍及警犬家人好<br />\n原因係如果唔咁做 對黑警係冇威脅 俾唔到壓力佢地<br />\n另一方面 佢地又好似冇得選擇自己既父母 對佢地好唔公平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且有啲警察仔女都係有出力有落場既手足<br />\n所以我建議要諗一個折衷方法 有條件咁排斥警察既仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個同學或者朋友對件事點睇佢地平時應該會係言談間直接間接咁表達出嚟 如果作為黑警後代都繼續維護自己父母犯既暴行咁就自然唔洗俾面 即管盡情羞辱佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係了解過之後發現真係自己手足既話咁就無謂自傷殘殺 但係都要俾到佢地警察家人壓力喎 咁點做呢<br />\n咁就靠佢地自己係警察家人面前吹係學校俾人點排擠 俾人恰得幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個應該係一個比較完美既方法去達到預期既效果又唔會另外敵立新既敵人或者手足相殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf1fa651d07544b6336867a52b8e770918e4321","tid":1492124,"uid":2562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMcAke7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMcAke7.png&h=5d1306ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae5318273f709d36d56c80b60955c12a8a83b9b4","tid":1492124,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"d74852dde43bb11958565959927e487ec62a4e37","tid":1492124,"uid":74442,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"人必先自侮而後人侮之<br />\n要怪就怪自己雙親<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8876da2d781c6d7fed87d2e0f8b39377f0c66721","tid":1492124,"uid":305357,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"認同樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近多咗咁多post，狗狗係咪好驚啊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比狗同狗乸教出嚟智商可以有幾高？<br />\n<br />\n醒既就會同同學仔一齊鬧鳩黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實唔會比人杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好似自己父母深藍我都可以深黃咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過蠢既真係抵撚死，<br />\n分分鐘大個做返狗，<br />\n仲講禍不及家人個啲左膠自己去同狗仔圍爐啦"},{"pid":"0bb85c38955d798f042f749111c5c2ec8cc621b6","tid":1492124,"uid":144594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d74852dde43bb11958565959927e487ec62a4e37","tid":1492124,"uid":74442,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"人必先自侮而後人侮之<br />\n要怪就怪自己雙親<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"但我都覺得要俾啲咁唔好彩出世係黑警家庭既手足投誠 係真手足就自然會反對佢地屋企人做黑警 唔洗我地再做啲咩學藍絲話齋 唔係撐自己屋企人做黑警怕咩俾人排斥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9158aebb42e9dc4f72e08ace7d093ada00e7e354","tid":1492124,"uid":70964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c206afc73cd0e69c2176b96f25a968d8f3359302","tid":1492124,"uid":144594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"好多人都好糾結應唔應該禍及警犬家人好<br />\n原因係如果唔咁做 對黑警係冇威脅 俾唔到壓力佢地<br />\n另一方面 佢地又好似冇得選擇自己既父母 對佢地好唔公平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且有啲警察仔女都係有出力有落場既手足<br />\n所以我建議要諗一個折衷方法 有條件咁排斥警察既仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個同學或者朋友對件事點睇佢地平時應該會係言談間直接間接咁表達出嚟 如果作為黑警後代都繼續維護自己父母犯既暴行咁就自然唔洗俾面 即管盡情羞辱佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係了解過之後發現真係自己手足既話咁就無謂自傷殘殺 但係都要俾到佢地警察家人壓力喎 咁點做呢<br />\n咁就靠佢地自己係警察家人面前吹係學校俾人點排擠 俾人恰得幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個應該係一個比較完美既方法去達到預期既效果又唔會另外敵立新既敵人或者手足相殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"一定要恥笑佢地 , 例如<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1) 你老豆老母係黑警 = 黑社會 好羞恥<br />\n2) 你老豆玩女人<br />\n3) 你老母比黑警屌<br />\n4) 你有冇比黑警屌過屎忽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">根本唔駛比面 <br />\n佢驚就同佢講 <br />\n1) 驚就唔好出街<br />\n2) 留係香港做乜 , 滾去大灣區讀書喇 香港人唔撚歡迎你<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">直至警隊解散</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9d6300bae3991a28e0bafd45d9d56383086018a","tid":1492124,"uid":63118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTim